{
  "episode_id": "2026-07-01",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，欢迎收听AI每日先锋，我是晓晓。今天是2026年7月1日，2026年下半年正式开启啦。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 9.927,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "大家好，我是博文。晓晓，这大半年过完了，你有什么感觉？",
      "start": 11.376,
      "duration": 4.18,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我的感觉就是……AI这个赛道越来越像一条高速公路了，而且这条高速正在被整个重铺。",
      "start": 16.053,
      "duration": 8.62,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个比喻有意思。重铺什么？",
      "start": 25.126,
      "duration": 2.395,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你想啊，从最底层的内存、芯片，到中间跑着的各种AI Agent，整条技术栈都在被重新定义。我今天早上刷新闻的时候，脑子里就蹦出来一句话——AI基础设施正在全面成熟和重构。",
      "start": 27.926,
      "duration": 17.26,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，这个观察很敏锐。那咱们今天就顺着这条线，好好聊聊。",
      "start": 45.619,
      "duration": 5.094,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好嘞，那先聊一个让我特别震撼的。博文，你听说了吗？华尔街现在把美光捧成了\"下一个英伟达\"。",
      "start": 51.178,
      "duration": 9.273,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "看到了。美光市值一度冲上去，超过了特斯拉和Meta。",
      "start": 60.913,
      "duration": 4.615,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，超过了特斯拉！我看到那个数字的时候下巴都快掉了。博文，这事你怎么看？一家做内存的公司，怎么突然就成了AI的核心资产了？",
      "start": 65.979,
      "duration": 11.842,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "其实这个逻辑特别清楚。你回想一下过去两三年，整个AI行业最值钱的故事是什么？是英伟达的GPU，因为大家都在抢算力。",
      "start": 78.321,
      "duration": 10.101,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，显卡，显卡，显卡。",
      "start": 88.86,
      "duration": 2.482,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "但现在问题来了——模型越做越大，参数从千亿跑到万亿，推理请求又多到离谱，GPU算得再快，数据喂不进去也白搭。这就是所谓的\"内存墙\"。",
      "start": 91.803,
      "duration": 12.016,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "等等等等，\"内存墙\"？这是什么意思？",
      "start": 104.264,
      "duration": 3.875,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "简单说就是，GPU这个厨房很大，灶台火力很猛，但冰箱太小，食材根本供不上来，厨师只能干等。",
      "start": 108.613,
      "duration": 8.62,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哦——那这个HBM，就是给AI装了个超大冰箱？",
      "start": 117.66,
      "duration": 4.528,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "没错，而且这个冰箱非常贵，技术门槛也极高。HBM的带宽、堆叠层数、良率，每一项都是硬功夫。所以华尔街的逻辑很直白：谁控制了AI的\"冰箱\"，谁就掐住了下一个瓶颈。",
      "start": 122.652,
      "duration": 15.325,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我懂了。以前大家觉得内存是周期股，价格涨涨跌跌看心情，现在突然发现，它变成了AI基础设施里那个不可替代的一环。",
      "start": 138.394,
      "duration": 13.105,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你这个总结很到位。这其实也是整个半导体格局在重新洗牌，从\"算力为王\"往\"存力为王\"迁移。",
      "start": 151.935,
      "duration": 8.141,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "涨知识了涨知识了。所以以后看AI公司，不能光盯着谁买了多少张显卡，还得看他的内存供应链稳不稳。",
      "start": 160.493,
      "duration": 8.664,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "是这个意思。",
      "start": 169.653,
      "duration": 0.958,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "行，这个事我记住了。哎博文，说到基础设施重构，还有一件事更让我觉得科幻。",
      "start": 171.023,
      "duration": 7.576,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哪个？",
      "start": 179.078,
      "duration": 0.61,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "明略科技开源了一个叫Octo的东西，说是要让AI Agent之间能互相通信和协作。博文，这个事你了解吗？",
      "start": 180.12,
      "duration": 9.927,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "了解。我今天特意去翻了一下他们的技术文档。",
      "start": 190.515,
      "duration": 4.136,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "那你给我翻译翻译，这个Octo到底是个啥？",
      "start": 195.141,
      "duration": 4.267,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你知道HTTP协议吧？就是当年让所有网页能互相连起来、最终形成万维网的那个底层规则。",
      "start": 199.885,
      "duration": 8.882,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个我知道，没有HTTP就没有互联网。",
      "start": 209.185,
      "duration": 4.18,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对。Octo做的事情，本质上就是在AI Agent的世界里，造一个类似的标准化通信协议。在这之前，每个Agent都是孤岛，你要让两个AI互相配合，得自己写一堆胶水代码。",
      "start": 213.804,
      "duration": 14.082,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，听起来就累。",
      "start": 228.298,
      "duration": 2.003,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "但有了Octo，Agent之间可以用统一语言对话，能发现彼此、能协作、能组成临时团队。这就不只是工具升级了，是整个AI应用架构在变。",
      "start": 230.794,
      "duration": 11.712,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我的天。你这么一说我脑子里画面就出来了——以前AI是一个个单独的APP，现在它们开始像微信好友一样互加好友了？",
      "start": 242.915,
      "duration": 10.144,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈，这个比喻虽然不太精确，但意思很接近。更准确地说，它更像是一个Agent的\"社交网络\"，甚至将来可能形成Agent之间的\"互联网\"。",
      "start": 253.546,
      "duration": 9.448,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这也太疯狂了。那这对我们普通人意味着什么？",
      "start": 263.436,
      "duration": 3.788,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "意味着以后你可能不用在十个AI工具之间来回切了。一个Agent帮你做完需求拆解，自动调度其他Agent去执行，最后给你交付结果。",
      "start": 267.684,
      "duration": 10.536,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哇，这不就是……未来的SaaS形态都要被重写了吗？",
      "start": 278.691,
      "duration": 5.79,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "不止SaaS，组织协作方式，甚至数字经济的规则，都可能跟着变。这是个范式级别的转移。",
      "start": 284.893,
      "duration": 7.706,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "好家伙，今天信息量已经够大了。咱俩稍微喘口气，来看几条有意思的短消息。",
      "start": 293.044,
      "duration": 7.445,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_037_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_037_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好。",
      "start": 300.944,
      "duration": 0.522,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_038_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_038_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "先说一条跟我们刚才聊的\"基础设施\"特别相关的。中国信通院发了一个AI基础设施的运维评测基准。",
      "start": 301.906,
      "duration": 10.928,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_039_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_039_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这个消息我注意到了。",
      "start": 313.312,
      "duration": 1.393,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_040_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_040_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "它覆盖了5款主流的国产芯片。那博文你怎么看？信通院做这个事，意义在哪？",
      "start": 315.186,
      "duration": 8.446,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_041_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_041_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你想啊，国产芯片这么多，每家都说自己行，但到底行不行，得有个统一的尺子来量。信通院出这个基准，就等于给整个国产AI Infra立了一个\"体检标准\"。",
      "start": 324.058,
      "duration": 13.148,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_042_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_042_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 43,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "明白了。相当于以前大家各夸各的，现在开始有客观成绩单了。",
      "start": 337.676,
      "duration": 7.227,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_043_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_043_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 44,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，这对国产替代的推进是非常关键的一步。",
      "start": 345.364,
      "duration": 4.049,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_044_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_044_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
