        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 47,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "100天啊博文！从创意到落地，这也太快了吧？",
      "start": 365.658,
      "duration": 5.05,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_047_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_047_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 48,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "这恰恰说明，AI硬件的创业门槛在被快速拉低。以前你做硬件，光开模、供应链就得折腾大半年。现在有了成熟的AI能力、开源模型、加上模块化的硬件方案，团队可以非常快地验证一个产品想法。",
      "start": 371.115,
      "duration": 16.433,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_048_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_048_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 49,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "所以说\"百天造机\"本身不是重点，重点是这个速度背后代表的新一代硬件创业范式。",
